  <entry>
    <title>应用层-DNS系统</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/04/02/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DNS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/04/02/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DNS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</id>
    <published>2022-04-02T11:13:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-12T10:00:27.299Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="DNS系统"><a href="#DNS系统" class="headerlink" title="DNS系统"></a>DNS系统</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021906692.png" alt="image-20220402190632554"></p><ul><li>通过IP地址这个全球唯一的标识符，完成通信。</li><li>IP地址太长不容易记忆，所以用域名代替。</li><li>由DNS完成从域名到IP地址的转换。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021907875.png" alt="image-20220402190757742"></p><h2 id="域名"><a href="#域名" class="headerlink" title="域名"></a>域名</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021910304.png" alt="image-20220402191028172"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021910738.png" alt="image-20220402191048617"></p><h2 id="域名服务器"><a href="#域名服务器" class="headerlink" title="域名服务器"></a>域名服务器</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021914264.png" alt="image-20220402191452130"></p><h2 id="域名解析过程"><a href="#域名解析过程" class="headerlink" title="域名解析过程"></a>域名解析过程</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021917098.png" alt="image-20220402191708947"></p><ul><li>递归查询：本地请求根服务器，根请求顶级，顶级请求权限……</li><li>迭代查询：本地请求根，本地请求顶级，本地请求权限……</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021919515.png" alt="image-20220402191930379"></p><ul><li>高速缓存用来存放最近查过的域名记录。</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
