  <entry>
    <title>传输层的四种功能</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/04/02/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/04/02/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</id>
    <published>2022-04-02T11:11:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-12T10:00:27.299Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="TCP连接管理"><a href="#TCP连接管理" class="headerlink" title="TCP连接管理"></a>TCP连接管理</h1><h2 id="连接建立三次握手"><a href="#连接建立三次握手" class="headerlink" title="连接建立三次握手"></a>连接建立三次握手</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021734028.png" alt="image-20220402173424892"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021738736.png" alt="image-20220402173824598"></p><ul><li>有大写的ACK就一定有小写的ack。</li></ul><h2 id="三次握手引发的SYN洪范攻击问题"><a href="#三次握手引发的SYN洪范攻击问题" class="headerlink" title="三次握手引发的SYN洪范攻击问题"></a>三次握手引发的SYN洪范攻击问题</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021740244.png" alt="image-20220402174019108"></p><ul><li>发送大量的请求连接报文段消耗资源。</li><li>解决方案：使用SYN cookie。</li></ul><h2 id="连接释放四次握手"><a href="#连接释放四次握手" class="headerlink" title="连接释放四次握手"></a>连接释放四次握手</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021741090.png" alt="image-20220402174130957"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021744535.png" alt="image-20220402174436391"></p><ul><li>等待2MSL是为了避免确认报文段丢失。</li></ul><h1 id="TCP可靠传输"><a href="#TCP可靠传输" class="headerlink" title="TCP可靠传输"></a>TCP可靠传输</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021745432.png" alt="image-20220402174554301"></p><h2 id="可靠传输机制"><a href="#可靠传输机制" class="headerlink" title="可靠传输机制"></a>可靠传输机制</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021747759.png" alt="image-20220402174705635"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021749201.png" alt="image-20220402174937070"></p><ul><li>确认号字段为希望收到的下一个报文段序号。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021750649.png" alt="image-20220402175032519"></p><h3 id="重传"><a href="#重传" class="headerlink" title="重传"></a>重传</h3><ol><li>超时重传。</li><li>基于冗余ACK的快速重传。</li></ol><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021754622.png" alt="image-20220402175440479"></p><h1 id="TCP流量控制"><a href="#TCP流量控制" class="headerlink" title="TCP流量控制"></a>TCP流量控制</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021758735.png" alt="image-20220402175812597"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021803296.png" alt="image-20220402180308148"></p><h1 id="TCP拥塞控制"><a href="#TCP拥塞控制" class="headerlink" title="TCP拥塞控制"></a>TCP拥塞控制</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021806047.png" alt="image-20220402180654918"></p><ul><li>多台服务器对接收方发送数据过多造成的拥塞。</li></ul><h2 id="控制拥塞的四种算法"><a href="#控制拥塞的四种算法" class="headerlink" title="控制拥塞的四种算法"></a>控制拥塞的四种算法</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021808181.png" alt="image-20220402180846043"></p><h2 id="慢开始和拥塞避免"><a href="#慢开始和拥塞避免" class="headerlink" title="慢开始和拥塞避免"></a>慢开始和拥塞避免</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021812072.png" alt="image-20220402181230935"></p><ul><li>ssthresh门限值。</li><li>新的门限值等于拥塞窗口除以2.</li></ul><h2 id="快重传和快恢复"><a href="#快重传和快恢复" class="headerlink" title="快重传和快恢复"></a>快重传和快恢复</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021815643.png" alt="image-20220402181534506"></p>]]></content>
    
    
