    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="IP组播"><a href="#IP组播" class="headerlink" title="IP组播"></a>IP组播</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021106033.png" alt="image-20220402110642849"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021107945.png" alt="image-20220402110726799"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021107918.png" alt="image-20220402110739774"></p><ul><li>组播路由器指可以运行组播协议的路由器。</li></ul><h2 id="IP组播地址"><a href="#IP组播地址" class="headerlink" title="IP组播地址"></a>IP组播地址</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021234962.png" alt="image-20220402123417780"></p><ul><li>D类地址用于组播或多播。</li><li>IP组播地址只能作为目的地址。</li><li>源地址一定是单播地址。</li></ul><h2 id="硬件组播"><a href="#硬件组播" class="headerlink" title="硬件组播"></a>硬件组播</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021348889.png" alt="image-20220402134812729"></p><ul><li>映射到MAC地址时只有最后23位不同。</li><li>丢弃是为了避免中间5位不一样而别的数据一样的情况。</li></ul><h2 id="IGMP协议与组播路由选择协议"><a href="#IGMP协议与组播路由选择协议" class="headerlink" title="IGMP协议与组播路由选择协议"></a>IGMP协议与组播路由选择协议</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021351869.png" alt="image-20220402135126730"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021352576.png" alt="image-20220402135241423"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021352551.png" alt="image-20220402135257430"></p><ul><li>网络层的上层。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021354886.png" alt="image-20220402135449722"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021355453.png" alt="image-20220402135530328"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021356662.png" alt="image-20220402135615508"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021356584.png" alt="image-20220402135634438"></p><h1 id="脑图时刻"><a href="#脑图时刻" class="headerlink" title="脑图时刻"></a>脑图时刻</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204021357854.png" alt="image-20220402135702729"></p>]]></content>
    
    
