  <entry>
    <title>IPv4-DHCP协议和ICMP协议</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/03/31/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DHCP%E5%92%8CICMP%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/03/31/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/DHCP%E5%92%8CICMP%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</id>
    <published>2022-03-31T09:24:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-12T10:00:27.299Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="DHCP协议"><a href="#DHCP协议" class="headerlink" title="DHCP协议"></a>DHCP协议</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311559308.png" alt="image-20220331155944137"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311606623.png" alt="image-20220331160605447"></p><ul><li>DHCP是应用层协议哦~</li></ul><h1 id="ICMP协议"><a href="#ICMP协议" class="headerlink" title="ICMP协议"></a>ICMP协议</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311608115.png" alt="image-20220331160814986"></p><ul><li>ICMP起一个桥梁的作用，更好地转发IP数据报…</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311611004.png" alt="image-20220331161104859"></p><ul><li>将出错的分组丢弃后发送一个ICMP差错报告。</li></ul><h2 id="ICMP差错报告报文"><a href="#ICMP差错报告报文" class="headerlink" title="ICMP差错报告报文"></a>ICMP差错报告报文</h2><p> <img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311614900.png" alt="image-20220331161445718"></p><ul><li>第二种现在已经取消了，不再用了。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311615930.png" alt="image-20220331161516770"></p><ul><li>ICMP差错报告报文是一个IP数据报，    是网络层传输单元的数据部分。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311618795.png" alt="image-20220331161815656"></p><ul><li>组播：是一点到多点，有选择性。</li><li>广播：是一点到所有节点。</li></ul><h2 id="ICMP询问报文"><a href="#ICMP询问报文" class="headerlink" title="ICMP询问报文"></a>ICMP询问报文</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311619298.png" alt="image-20220331161947150"></p><ul><li>具体的应用：ping 网址</li><li>后两种现在已经不再使用了。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311621030.png" alt="image-20220331162126889"></p>]]></content>
    
    
