    <title>IPv4-ARP协议</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/03/31/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/ARP%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/03/31/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/ARP%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</id>
    <published>2022-03-31T09:23:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-12T10:00:27.299Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ARP协议"><a href="#ARP协议" class="headerlink" title="ARP协议"></a>ARP协议</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311131765.png" alt="image-20220331113148625"></p><ul><li>ARP高速缓存内存放的是本局域网内的mac地址。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311138624.png" alt="image-20220331113844482"></p><h1 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h1><p>ARP协议帮助找到MAC地址。</p><p>处于链路层和网络层中间的协议，结合了IP地址和MAC地址。</p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311142994.png" alt="image-20220331114218824"></p><ul><li>ARP自动进行用户不知道。</li></ul><h2 id="习题"><a href="#习题" class="headerlink" title="习题"></a>习题</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203311144642.png" alt="image-20220331114426503"></p>]]></content>
    
    
