  <entry>
    <title>IPv4-网络地址转换与子网划分</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/03/30/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%90%E7%BD%91%E5%88%92%E5%88%86/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/03/30/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%90%E7%BD%91%E5%88%92%E5%88%86/</id>
    <published>2022-03-30T12:22:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-12T10:00:27.299Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="网络地址转换（NAT）"><a href="#网络地址转换（NAT）" class="headerlink" title="网络地址转换（NAT）"></a>网络地址转换（NAT）</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203301947189.png" alt="image-20220330194739059"></p><ul><li>即私有IP地址在外网中是无效的。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203301952422.png" alt="image-20220330195209253"></p><h1 id="子网划分"><a href="#子网划分" class="headerlink" title="子网划分"></a>子网划分</h1><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203301954891.png" alt="image-20220330195400751"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203301955281.png" alt="image-20220330195544145"></p><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203301956237.png" alt="image-20220330195657077"></p><h2 id="子网掩码"><a href="#子网掩码" class="headerlink" title="子网掩码"></a>子网掩码</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203302000044.png" alt="image-20220330200023909"></p><ul><li>子网掩码的前两位为全1，最后一位为全0</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203302003598.png" alt="image-20220330200332441"></p><ul><li>IP地址的前两位与子网掩码的全1相与数字不变，最后一位与全0相与得0，所以重点是看第三位。</li></ul><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202204041548780.png" alt="image-20220330201306511"></p><ul><li>通过子网掩码看出主机号占几位。</li><li>广播地址的主机号为全1，全1即是十进制的255.</li></ul><h2 id="使用子网的分组转发"><a href="#使用子网的分组转发" class="headerlink" title="使用子网的分组转发"></a>使用子网的分组转发</h2><p><img src="https://www.halisi7.space/202203302024431.png" alt="image-20220330202401285"></p>]]></content>
    
    
